{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-notes-js","path":"/notes/kedro-preflight/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a36259ec-cf14-5724-8e80-2e7735f398a1","html":"<p>This is a very rough idea for a kedro package to prevent time lost to get partway through a pipeline run only to realize that you dont have access to data or resources.</p>\n<h1>Must Haves</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>check that inputs exist or are of a type to skip (sql)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Good to haves</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>check that all input and output databases are accessible with good credentials</li>\n<li>check for s3 bucket access</li>\n<li>check for spark install</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Implementation</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token decorator annotation punctuation\">@hook_spec</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">before_pipeline_run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>run_params<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> pipeline<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> catalog<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>run params</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"run_id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> str\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"project_path\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"env\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"kedro_version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"tags\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"from_nodes\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"to_nodes\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"node_names\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"from_inputs\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"load_versions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>List<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"pipeline_name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"extra_params\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Optional<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Dict<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Any<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-09T15:01:00.000Z","title":"Kedro Preflight","description":"run checks before running the pipeline","path":"kedro-preflight","twitter_cover":null,"cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"a36259ec-cf14-5724-8e80-2e7735f398a1"}}}